{"tid":1569311,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我要代表所有連登仔多謝今日打人捉人嘅藍絲同警犬","createTime":"2019-09-14T14:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T15:01:37.000Z","uid":286190,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8332a8800cfc3ba1fa31da9d6cef5f024b6efe90","tid":1569311,"uid":286190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:35:53.000Z","msg":"昨夜個中秋和理非搞到個抗議氣氛淡曬<br />\n<br />\n多謝你地扑街今日搞事,打後生仔,亂捉人黎燒返着把火<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3OKOhg6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OKOhg6.jpg&h=a5259ded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班濕鳩仲以為10月1先開始大搞有用?今日打殘一個聽日拉一個,等到10月1醫返都曬藥費啦扑街。仲有幾多人到時可以同你搞?靠班左膠?不如直接移民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始話欖炒,結果船頭驚鬼船尾驚賊,放火又話驚民意,放蟲又話驚friendly fire,最好搞何式凝靜坐等班狗同藍絲打撚殘再拉入監,之後就可以和向國際扮可憐好唔好?<br />\n<br />\n你班廢青敢撚廢,比我係廢老都打柒你,又唔見烏克蘭支持政府班人敢日光日白打示威者,係升級就915升,升完我想睇仲有冇廢老撐警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915燒狗都唔割<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />靜坐和理非比人打,扮可憐啦扑街"},{"pid":"f586e23463e353813e030003dd6a47fa449c98e1","tid":1569311,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e491b848ba1fa759bb1d750b554d3af249aa6ff","tid":1569311,"uid":148580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"和理非覺醒味"},{"pid":"52dfb28a7e4f66c21ff4e00d9d46f52fff4a212f","tid":1569311,"uid":234159,"l